text: Wutach is a municipality in Waldshut in Baden-Württemberg, Germany. It has a administration community with the neighbouring town of Bonndorf im Schwarzwald. The municipality has villages of Ewattingen, Lembach and Münchingen. It has a primary school and kindergarten in Ewattingen. The current mayor is Alexander Pfliegensdörfer since 2023. Wutach is to the south of the Wutach Gorge, which flows through the river Wutach. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Waldshut (district)
